    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This specification defines the addressing architecture of the IP Version 6 (IPv6) protocol.  The document includes the IPv6 addressing model, text representations of IPv6 addresses, definition of IPv6 unicast addresses, anycast addresses, and multicast addresses, and an IPv6 node's required addresses. [STANDARDS-TRACK]&lt;/p&gt;</t>
